<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Just days after going public with their relationship, Rebel Wilson shared a series of loved-up photos with her new boyfriend, multi-millionaire Jacob Busch.  </p>

<p>In images posted to Instagram, the 40-year-old actress shared a passionate kiss with her new beau.</p>

<p>The couple were seen lying next to each other, with Rebel planting a kiss on the 29-year-old heir to the Anheuser-Busch brewing dynasty, which produces Budweiser beer.</p>

<p>Sealed with a kiss: Just days after going public with their relationship, Rebel Wilson shared a series of loved-up photos with her new boyfriend, multi-millionaire Jacob Busch</p>

<p>In a second photo, the Pitch Perfect star cuddled up to her handsome new boyfriend, who is estimated to be worth a whopping $140million.</p>

<p>While the couple is yet to address their fledgling relationship, they made headlines last week when they debuted their romance in Monaco.</p>

